I am a top rated Duda Website Designer. I have more then 5 years of experience on Duda, I have designed more then 500 websites over Duda.
I can design any website on Duda from scratch . 
I can customize any template. I can create new templates.
I have experience of all Duda widgets, I can add custom HTML,CSS & JS.

reviews.comment:
Exceptional, absolutely exceptional. Sudhir works really fast, but with great accuracy. He is proficient at using Duda, and for this job, duplicating a website design inside of Duda (wire frame) he did a fabulous job. I would highly recommend him, but do not order from him, as I want him free to work on more projects I have...LOL!

Thank Sudhir!!

Sudhir Kumar delivered EXCELLENT work on our website development project with top-notch documentation and code expertise. Highly recommend him for any web development needs dealing with the Duda platform!  We are looking forward to the next project.

Great Job! We needed a website copied to Duda and he delivered.  I've used him twice for this and each time, he delivered exactly what we were looking for.  He knows what he is doing with Duda and makes it easy.
Sudhir did an excellent job. I'm in the process of a reorder. And will order again in the future. Sudhir should be your first choice if you're considering a gig worker to work on your Duda site.

Working with Sudhir Kumar on my website development project was an absolute pleasure! His professionalism and ability to exceed expectations were impressive, while his cooperative nature and quick, polite responses made the process seamless. A JOB WELL DONE!
